&lt;p>We hear very commonly that you don&amp;rsquo;t go to extreme of anything in the life, &lt;br>
Walk the middle path, settle on middle ground, Madhya Maarga. &lt;br>
Yet, no matter how hard we try, living on the middle path seems unsustainable. &lt;br>
The more we force ourselves to stay within its confines, &lt;br>
life becomes increasingly mundane and devoid of meaning.&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>